":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"痰伯人品點 去唔去&ldquo;玩&rdquo;<br />\n相信自有公論<br />\n<br />\n天氣有正氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5739a8e300e1d879448394254cd446007b0a402","tid":528772,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b332ad8deadb73d9ed28bddf165318f676ae86e","tid":528772,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e7db1b42ddc569dc01fb5b5f1d51d29f5e34bcb8","tid":528772,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82c8bcb053fe537211b7bf1a4020190f9fed4d14","tid":528772,"uid":17103,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:04:12.000Z","msg":"成個中國娛樂圈得廿年唔夠既歷史, 屌你教乜撚野母. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  識你老鼠咩.<br />\n<br />\n又係 D 大陸閪夜狼自大, 矮仔同 25 做緊娛樂圈時你班撚樣玩緊小紅簿渣教母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"關娛樂圈歷史咩事呀？要講輩份呢啲？學大飛話齋，洗唔洗由少林五祖講起呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  教母呢個字就已經係輩份同地位, 唔講輩份洗鬼提教母呢兩個字咩<br />\n同講 &quot;我最撚憎人講粗口&quot; 有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n少林五祖講起就唔洗, 呢個 Grace 呢就 90 年代先出頭.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/01/11/phpjv1s1r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F01%2F11%2Fphpjv1s1r.jpg&h=0ae53df5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGrace Han 八十年代都重係做緊廠整手袋, 係之後九十年代鬼佬想係中國搞超模大賽先搵佢接頭<br />\n佢身份咪就係香港 D 買辦一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上面重有人話國際知名度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己 Google 下 Grace Han 同 Supermodel 或者 Model 睇下幾個 Result 啦<br />\n<br />\n呢篇文個 Topic 將&quot;中國&quot;個字刪左已經好大問題, 你要夜狼自大都加返中國啦. 關香港鳩事咩.<br />\n<br />\n長州球王陳金水帶住對長州隊去巴西 D 街場踢波, 唔通巴西 D 小報會話球王陳金水咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&quot; 韓穎華稍早進一步暗諷曾志偉，她說：「有人私信來，叫老婆子挺住。」她說，兵來將擋、水來土掩，「<span style=\"color: red;\">早就想公開這件事，好萊塢製片大老被眾多著名女星公開曝光後，老婆子（指她自己）就想幾時有人爆香港賤人惡行啊？</span>」韓穎華認為，不敢說不會有事，「<span style=\"color: red;\">但有事臨到，老婆子也不會逃避，敢做敢當，為非作歹的人有幾個在法庭認罪的？沒有！</span>」&quot;<br />\n<br />\n同 #metoo 撚一樣, 水就識抽. \u001b矮仔同 25 大陸無人敢郁你咩? <br />\n如果係真知道又唔講, 你咪重撚衰過欄后?"},{"pid":"d26ba91e123aaf81b6196483b18a9ceff00ebf1d","tid":528772,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"人格擔保吖嗱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6418ba7a926ed71edc971c52588eea9bdc3d8e63","tid":528772,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"有幾成人信今次呢餅帶係堅野, 唔係剪接片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4754bf11a887e63c01a8e6000aafa8b851197b70","tid":528772,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6418ba7a926ed71edc971c52588eea9bdc3d8e63","tid":528772,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"有幾成人信今次呢餅帶係堅野, 唔係剪接片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"我有獨家料, 所以信今次呢餅帶係堅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720ee5c6c40f3c9f165b21df4ab7d7126042c543","tid":528772,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8861a1f33b4fc419c0f02c10a380fb286ac94c7","tid":528772,"uid":93217,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"細個有親戚喺大富豪做侍應，有一次見大歌星去玩，買咗條女街鐘出街。條女第二日返嚟屌晒鬼，話搞完嘢，走嘅時候問大歌星攞肉金，佢唔肯俾，話自己係